nodes.text: Ariana Surabat was a plucky female explorer who flew the starship Ravenstar with her crew. She founded the planet Batuu in the Outer Rim Territories. The Surabat River Valley on Batuu was named after her.
Ariana Surabat was first created for Star Wars: Galaxy's Edge, which opened to guests at Disneyland Park on May 31, 2019.
